      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Reinventing the Wheel",
        "Client": "Desert Inventor",
        "Description": "Wheels get stuck in the sand,\r\nlimiting trade across deserts;\r\nand yet, Volvidon traverse the\r\nPlains with ease\u2014wait, that\u0027s\r\nit! Allow me to observe how a\r\nVolvidon rolls, and I shall\r\ndesign an unstoppable wheel!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Volvidon",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "R\u00E9inventer la roue",
        "Client": "Inventeur du d\u00E9sert",
        "Description": "Les roues s\u0027enlisent dans\r\nle sable, \u00E7a limite les\r\nd\u00E9placements dans le d\u00E9sert.\r\nPas pour les Volvidon par\r\ncontre ! Si je pouvais voir un\r\nVolvidon rouler, je pourrais\r\ninventer une nouvelle roue !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Volvidon",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Reinventare la ruota",
        "Client": "Inventore del deserto",
        "Description": "Le ruote si bloccano nella\r\nsabbia, limitando il commercio\r\nnel deserto. Eppure i Volvidon\r\nattraversano le piane con\r\nfacilit\u00E0. Vorrei vedere come\r\nrotola un Volvidon per creare\r\nuna ruota inarrestabile.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Volvidon",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Das Rad neu erfinden",
        "Client": "W\u00FCstenerfinder",
        "Description": "R\u00E4der bleiben im Sand stecken,\r\nwas den Handel in der W\u00FCste\r\neinschr\u00E4nkt. Volvidon kennen\r\ndieses Problem nicht-- ... Das\r\nist es! Wenn ich studiere, wie\r\nsie sich kugeln, kann ich ein\r\nunaufhaltsames Rad bauen!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Volvidon.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Reinventando la rueda",
        "Client": "Inventor del desierto",
        "Description": "Las ruedas se hunden en la\r\narena; eso dificulta las rutas\r\npor el desierto. Pero los\r\nVolvidon surcan los llanos\r\nsin dif... Espera, \u00A1eso es!\r\nConsigue que pueda ver uno,\r\n\u00A1y crear\u00E9 una rueda imparable!",
        "Target": "Caza un Volvidon",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0418\u0437\u043E\u0431\u0440\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0438 \u043A\u043E\u043B\u0435\u0441\u043E",
        "Client": "\u041F\u0443\u0441\u0442\u044B\u043D\u043D\u044B\u0439 \u0438\u0437\u043E\u0431\u0440\u0435\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0435\u043B\u044C",
        "Description": "\u041A\u043E\u043B\u0435\u0441\u0430 \u0437\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0435\u0432\u0430\u044E\u0442 \u0432 \u043F\u0435\u0441\u043A\u0435,\r\n\u0438\u0437-\u0437\u0430 \u044D\u0442\u043E\u0433\u043E \u0442\u0440\u0443\u0434\u043D\u043E \u043F\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0432\u043E\u0437\u0438\u0442\u044C\r\n\u0442\u043E\u0432\u0430\u0440\u044B \u043F\u043E \u043F\u0443\u0441\u0442\u044B\u043D\u0435. \u0410 \u0432\u043E\u0442\r\n\u0412\u043E\u043B\u044C\u0432\u0438\u0434\u043E\u043D\u044B \u0441 \u043B\u0435\u0433\u043A\u043E\u0441\u0442\u044C\u044E\r\n\u043F\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0445\u043E\u0434\u044F\u0442 \u0420\u0430\u0432\u043D\u0438\u043D\u044B. \u0422\u043E\u0447\u043D\u043E! \u0414\u0430\u0439\r\n\u043F\u043E\u0441\u043C\u043E\u0442\u0440\u044E, \u043A\u0430\u043A \u043E\u043D\u0438 \u043A\u0430\u0442\u044F\u0442\u0441\u044F!\r\n\u042F \u043F\u0440\u0438\u0434\u0443\u043C\u0430\u044E \u043A\u043E\u043B\u0435\u0441\u043E \u0434\u043B\u044F \u043F\u0443\u0441\u0442\u044B\u043D\u0438!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0412\u043E\u043B\u044C\u0432\u0438\u0434\u043E\u043D\u0430",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
